2066
02:07:32,875 --> 02:07:35,625
Lissy… Her time's up.

2067
02:07:37,333 --> 02:07:38,291
She's gone.

2068
02:07:49,666 --> 02:07:52,041
I still remember the
day I delivered Lissy.

2069
02:07:53,750 --> 02:07:54,875
She was a premature baby…

2070
02:07:57,500 --> 02:08:01,375
