2103
02:11:19,416 --> 02:11:20,250
Sir?

2104
02:11:20,583 --> 02:11:21,916
Aradhya? My wife?

2105
02:11:23,166 --> 02:11:24,125
Hey, Johnson!

2106
02:11:24,791 --> 02:11:25,666
{\an8}What?

2107
02:11:25,750 --> 02:11:27,500
Did you see sir's wife
traveling in a boat?

2108
