It's getting late. Let's go.

2160
02:16:03,083 --> 02:16:04,583
I can't stay without her, dude.

2161
02:16:09,625 --> 02:16:16,000
<i>Like a Hibiscus flower</i>
<i>That burns in fire silently</i>

2162
